"Don't tell anyone. It's nothing."

730
00:54:40,110 --> 00:54:42,529
I think that's why

731
00:54:42,612 --> 00:54:46,491
he couldn't go to the police right away.

732
00:54:50,120 --> 00:54:54,082
Had the couple's kidnapping been reported
to the police sooner,

733
00:54:54,165 --> 00:54:56,334
they would have lived to see this day.

734
00:54:57,002 --> 00:54:59,379
Most kidnappings remain unsolved

735
00:54:59,462 --> 00:55:02,132
because citizens are reluctant
to report them.

736
00:55:02,632 --> 00:55:04,843
In the case of the murdered couple,

737
00:55:04,926 --> 00:55:09,222
the sales manager of Samjeong Machinery
didn't report it to the police

738
00:55:09,306 --> 00:55:12,100
after handing over
the 80 million won ransom.

739
00:55:12,183 --> 00:55:14,477
At first,
I went to report it to the police,

740
00:55:14,978 --> 00:55:18,231
but I got another call from the boss.

741
00:55:18,815 --> 00:55:20,900
He sounded very cheerful on the phone,

742
00:55:21,943 --> 00:55:23,987
so I was pretty relieved.

743
00:55:24,070 --> 00:55:27,699
Even though the kidnappers were present
at the scene of the handoff,

744
00:55:27,782 --> 00:55:29,909
there was nothing that could be done.

745
00:55:39,377 --> 00:55:43,214
So that night, we came back
without running into any danger.

746
00:55:44,090 --> 00:55:48,511
Kim Hyeon-yang got up first and said,
"Good work, boys."

747
00:55:51,181 --> 00:55:52,807
"Look, this is 80 million."

748
00:55:53,683 --> 00:55:58,438
"Imagine the trouble
we'd have to go through to make 80 million

749
00:55:58,521 --> 00:56:00,357
by working our tails off."

750
00:56:00,440 --> 00:56:03,693
They were chatting among themselves.

751
00:56:03,777 --> 00:56:06,988
They told the man,
"It's all good now. Have a drink with us."

752
00:56:07,072 --> 00:56:10,909
"After a good night's sleep,
you'll be back at your house tomorrow."

753
00:56:11,409 --> 00:56:13,620
"So don't you worry."

754
00:56:13,703 --> 00:56:16,331
Then the man laughed and replied,

755
00:56:17,374 --> 00:56:20,335
"Okay, thank you so much."

756
00:56:20,418 --> 00:56:22,921
And he had a few shots of soju.

757
00:56:27,133 --> 00:56:28,760
They said, "Well done."

758
00:56:28,843 --> 00:56:33,431
"Go stay with your wife while you wait."

759
00:56:33,515 --> 00:56:35,517
That's what they told him.

760
00:56:35,600 --> 00:56:40,230
But while they were drinking,
after sending the man back downstairs,

761
00:56:40,313 --> 00:56:42,607
I became the point of contention.

762
00:56:43,775 --> 00:56:46,569
They said, "Everything worked out well."

763
00:56:46,653 --> 00:56:48,780
"Good work, Hyo-jin."

764
00:56:48,863 --> 00:56:54,160
But then Moon Sang-rok suddenly yelled,
"We gotta kill this bitch too."

765
00:56:54,661 --> 00:56:56,371
He suddenly mentioned me.

766
00:56:56,996 --> 00:56:57,831
No.

767
00:56:59,999 --> 00:57:02,877
So Dong-eun initiated the murder, and…

768
00:57:04,170 --> 00:57:09,509
KIM HYEON-YANG, MOON SANG-ROK
CHIJON FAMILY MEMBERS

769
00:57:10,635 --> 00:57:14,973
