before he came back."

770
00:57:15,056 --> 00:57:16,683
Then Kim Hyeon-yang said,

771
00:57:16,766 --> 00:57:20,770
"We agreed to keep her alive.
We're men of our word, aren't we?"

772
00:57:21,312 --> 00:57:24,482
"We should remain loyal to each other."

773
00:57:24,566 --> 00:57:29,070
Moon Sang-rok said,
"You're crazy for this bitch, bastard."

774
00:57:29,737 --> 00:57:31,865
"You've gone crazy for this bitch."

775
00:57:31,948 --> 00:57:36,244
Then Kim Hyeon-yang yelled,
"What the hell did you say?"

776
00:57:37,579 --> 00:57:41,541
Then they started swearing and fighting,
grabbing each other by the collar,

777
00:57:41,624 --> 00:57:47,380
and Moon Sang-rok threw a bottle
with beer still in it.

778
00:57:54,137 --> 00:57:59,893
It hit Kim Hyeon-yang,
and his head began to bleed.

779
00:58:01,769 --> 00:58:07,484
At that moment,
I couldn't help but think it was all over.

780
00:58:07,567 --> 00:58:10,153
The air in that room was just terrifying.

781
00:58:10,778 --> 00:58:13,490
I thought,
"They are going to kill me today."

782
00:58:25,168 --> 00:58:29,005
She thought,
"If I don't run away from here, I'll die."

783
00:58:30,924 --> 00:58:34,928
I was most scared
of Kim Gi-hwan returning.

784
00:58:35,011 --> 00:58:36,930
I was overwhelmed by the stress

785
00:58:37,013 --> 00:58:41,518
of having to escape that place
before he was out of prison.

786
00:58:41,601 --> 00:58:42,435
So…

787
00:58:43,770 --> 00:58:46,397
Had she not survived,

788
00:58:46,481 --> 00:58:49,526
they could have gone on
to kill 100 people.

789
00:58:50,318 --> 00:58:54,864
I thought, "Should I hide out
in a pig pen? Or a barn?"

790
00:58:56,366 --> 00:58:59,869
She crawled under the platform
and hid there until sunset.

791
00:59:01,162 --> 00:59:03,623
Even after escaping,

792
00:59:03,706 --> 00:59:06,834
I didn't feel completely free
from their grasp.

793
00:59:06,918 --> 00:59:09,587
I thought if they searched for me
from town to town,

794
